":1,\"limit\":100},\"caller\":{\"type\":\"direct\"}}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":0,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":1472,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":58212,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":1472,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":0},\"output_tokens\":3,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"},\"context_management\":null},\"requestId\":\"req_011CZ32bSvLyc9Q4ViHck4ZM\",\"uuid\":\"b10e9c3f-ddc9-4559-aaa5-786678056d6a\"},\"type\":\"agent_progress\",\"prompt\":\"\",\"agentId\":\"ad280d77b06eee85c\"},\"toolUseID\":\"agent_msg_01KXEjdtqbh836zVhcQmKn5J\",\"parentToolUseID\":\"toolu_01XbDzeEdJRkoHyQPBpKCfKL\",\"uuid\":\"3e218f45-525f-4b7c-ae40-af4e26ab0886\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-03-14T13:10:46.725Z\",\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli\",\"sessionId\":\"6045d8ec-bf58-4e40-89fe-f1126e592103\",\"version\":\"2.1.76\",\"gitBranch\":\"feat/device-auth-login\",\"slug\":\"synthetic-puzzling-torvalds\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"3e218f45-525f-4b7c-ae40-af4e26ab0886\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"type\":\"progress\",\"data\":{\"message\":{\"type\":\"user\",\"message\":{\"role\":\"user\",\"content\":[{\"tool_use_id\":\"toolu_01HxR3Q6mpyrkbcNiagVc7c3\",\"type\":\"tool_result\",\"content\":\"     1‚Üí# Entire Development Environment\\n     2‚Üí\\n     3‚ÜíThis is a monorepo-style development environment that manages three interconnected repositories:\\n     4‚Üí- **devenv** (this repo): Orchestration scripts for local development\\n     5‚Üí- **entire**: Go backend with HTTP and gRPC APIs for git repository hosting, user management, and OAuth\\n     6‚Üí- **entire.io**: Rails BFF (Backend For Frontend) with React/TypeScript frontend\\n     7‚Üí\\n     8‚Üí## Architecture Overview\\n     9‚Üí\\n    10‚ÜíSee individual repository documentation for detailed architecture:\\n    11‚Üí- [entire backend architecture](./entire/CLAUDE.md)\\n    12‚Üí- [entire.io BFF and frontend architecture](./entire.io/CLAUDE.md)\\n    13‚Üí\\n    14‚Üí## Development Workflow\\n    15‚Üí\\n    16‚Üí### Starting the Environment\\n    17‚ÜíAlways use `mise run dev` from devenv root to start all services.\\n    18‚ÜíThis automatically:\\n    19‚Üí1. Starts entire backend (logs to entire.log)\\n    20‚Üí2. Waits for OAuth credentials to be generated\\n    21‚Üí3. Starts entire.io Rails + frontend (logs to entire.io.log)\\n    22‚Üí4. Creates default test user (username: test, password: password1234)\\n    23‚Üí\\n    24‚ÜíDefault test credentials: test / password1234\\n    25‚ÜíFrontend URL: http://localhost:5173/login\\n    26‚ÜíBackend URL: http://localhost:8080\\n    27‚Üí\\n    28‚Üí## Service Dependencies\\n    29‚Üí\\n    30‚Üí- entire.io DEPENDS on entire backend being running first\\n    31‚Üí- OAuth credentials are auto-generated by entire backend on startup\\n    32‚Üí- start-dev.sh handles this orchestration automatically\\n    33‚Üí\\n    34‚Üí### Port Allocation\\n    35‚Üí- entire backend: 8080\\n    36‚Üí- entire.io frontend: 5173\\n    37‚Üí\\n    38‚Üí## Making Changes Across Repositories\\n    39‚Üí\\n    40‚ÜíWhen a feature requires changes in multiple repos:\\n    41‚Üí\\n    42‚Üí### 1. API Contract Changes (entire backend ‚Üí entire.io BFF ‚Üí frontend)\\n    43‚Üí- Start in `entire/`: Update proto files or HTTP handlers (see [entire/CLAUDE.md](./entire/CLAUDE.md))\\n    44‚Üí- Update `entire.io/`: Modify controllers/services to use new API (see [entire.io/CLAUDE.md](./entire.io/CLAUDE.md))\\n    45‚Üí- Update `entire.io/frontend/`: Update React components/API calls\\n    46‚Üí- Test integration: Use `mise run dev` and verify in browser\\n    47‚Üí\\n    48‚Üí### 2. Authentication/OAuth Changes\\n    49‚Üí- Backend: `entire/internal/user/` and OAuth-related code\\n    50‚Üí- BFF: `entire.io/app/controllers/` (auth controllers)\\n    51‚Üí- Frontend: `entire.io/frontend/src/` (auth components/routes)\\n    52‚Üí- OAuth credentials flow through start-dev.sh automatically\\n    53‚Üí\\n    54‚Üí### 3. Git Operations\\n    55‚Üí- Backend implementation: `entire/internal/repo/`, `entire/internal/objectstore/`\\n    56‚Üí- BFF layer: `entire.io/app/controllers/repositories_controller.rb`\\n    57‚Üí- Frontend UI: `entire.io/frontend/src/components/` (repo-related)\\n    58‚Üí\\n    59‚Üí### 4. Testing Integration\\n    60‚Üí- Backend tests: Run in `entire/` directory using `mise run test`\\n    61‚Üí- BFF tests: Run in `entire.io/` directory using `mise run bff-tests`\\n    62‚Üí- Frontend tests: Run in `entire.io/frontend/` directory\\n    63‚Üí- Integration testing: There are some in `entire/` through `mise run test:integration` or start with `mise run dev` and test flows manually\\n    64‚Üí\\n    65‚Üí## Code Patterns for Cross-Repo Features\\n    66‚Üí\\n    67‚Üí### When Adding a New Feature\\n    68‚Üí1. Define gRPC/HTTP API in `entire/` if backend changes needed\\n    69‚Üí2. Implement backend logic in appropriate `entire/internal/` package\\n    70‚Üí3. Add Rails controller/service in `entire.io/app/`\\n    71‚Üí4. Create React components in `entire.io/frontend/src/components/`\\n    72‚Üí5. Add routes in `entire.io/frontend/src/routes/`\\n    73‚Üí6. Test end-to-end with `mise run dev`\\n    74‚Üí\\n    75‚Üí### When Modifying OAuth Flow\\n    76‚Üí- Backend: Check `entire/internal/user/` and auth handlers\\n    77‚Üí- OAuth clients file: `entire/data/.default-oauth-clients`\\n    78‚Üí- Environment variables: Set in start-dev.sh (ENTIRE_CLIENT_ID, etc.)\\n    79‚Üí- Frontend: OAuth redirect URLs and client ID in frontend .env\\n    80‚Üí\\n    81‚Üí## Things to Watch Out For\\n    82‚Üí\\n    83‚Üí### Data Directories\\n    84‚Üí- `entire/data/` contains runtime data (OAuth clients, raft state, git objects)\\n    85‚Üí- This directory is gitignored\\n    86‚Üí- Don't commit OAuth credentials or test data\\n    87‚Üí\\n    88‚Üí### Default Test User\\n    89‚Üí- Created automatically by start-dev.sh\\n    90‚